HEADWORD: Chert
<hw>Chert</hw> <pr>(ch⟦etil⟧rt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ir.
<ets>ceart</ets> stone, perh. akin to E. <ets>crag</ets>.]</ety>
